Kea Unbound DDNS

Automatically registers Kea DHCP leases and static reservations in the Unbound
DNS resolver. Runs an RFC 2136 DNS UPDATE stub listener for kea-dhcp-ddns (with
optional TSIG authentication) bound to 127.0.0.1, plus on-demand reservation and
lease synchronization, a DNS registration audit view, and scheduled stale-record
cleanup.

WWW: https://github.com/tkreagan/os-kea-unbound
